@startuml UEORMS_State_09
top to bottom direction
hide empty description
title UEORMS State Transition - 9) Projects and Timesheets

[*] --> ProjectPlanned
ProjectPlanned --> ProjectActive : approve baseline
ProjectActive --> MembersAssigned : assign resources
MembersAssigned --> TimesheetDraft : log time
TimesheetDraft --> TimesheetSubmitted : submit timesheet
TimesheetSubmitted --> TimesheetApproved : approve timesheet
TimesheetSubmitted --> TimesheetRejected : reject timesheet
TimesheetRejected --> TimesheetDraft : fix and resubmit
TimesheetApproved --> ProgressUpdated : update milestones/budgets
ProgressUpdated --> ProjectDashboardUpdated : refresh dashboard
ProjectDashboardUpdated --> [*]

@enduml
